com.tsgrp.migration.queue

Class MigrationQueueWatchFolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.queue.AbstractMigrationQueue
      • com.tsgrp.migration.queue.MigrationQueueWatchFolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MigrationQueue

    public class MigrationQueueWatchFolder
extends AbstractMigrationQueue
    Monitors the injected watchFolder for files that do not match the lockFileExtension. Continually creates queue items until there are no more items in the watch folder. Supports multiple threads and instances of OpenMigrate operating on the same watch folder.
